article.description: — Christyon Eugene had 17 points in Troy's 87-64 win against Tennessee Tech on Saturday night.
article.headline: Eugene powers Troy to 87-64 victory over Tennessee Tech
article.linkText: Eugene powers Troy to 87-64 victory over Tennessee Tech
article.story:
TROY, Ala. -- — Christyon Eugene had 17 points in Troy's 87-64 win against Tennessee Tech on Saturday night.

Eugene was 6 of 9 shooting, including 1 for 3 from distance, and went 4 for 4 from the line for the Trojans (7-4). Zay Williams added 15 points while shooting 6 of 11 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line, and he also had eight rebounds. Nelson Phillips recorded 13 points.

Brett Thompson and Tyrone Perry scored 13 apiece to pace the Golden Eagles (3-7). Jayvis Harvey had 12 points, seven rebounds and two steals.

------
